dct_title_s: South East Asia : oil and gas activity and concession map 2020.
dct_description_sm: Bathymetry and gradient tints. Includes general legend, statistical tables, graphs, charts and color advertisements. "(Map data correct as of October 2020)". Shows gas fields, oil fields, gas pipelines, oil pipelines, refineries, concession blocks.
